OL,3,CBridgerton star Nicola Coughlan has
OL,4,C'no interest in body positivity'
OL,6,FBridgerton star Nicola Coughlan has
OL,7,Fsaid she has "no interest in body
OL,8,Fpositivity" and that she finds it
OL,9,F"boring" when people talk about her
OL,10,Fsize.
OL,12,FThe Irish actress, 39, known for
OL,13,Fplaying panicky student Clare Devlin
OL,14,Fon Channel 4 comedy Derry Girls, stars
OL,15,Fin the Netflix regency series
OL,16,FBridgerton as Penelope Bridgerton.
OL,18,FDespite the success of the show, she
OL,19,Fhas described how disappointing it is
OL,20,Fthat so many people praise her body
OL,21,Fsize and talk about her weight.
OL,26,@oD@NOUpD@KO]qD@AOUqD@HO]
