OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772679804
OL,3,CBridgerton star Nicola Coughlan has
OL,4,C'no interest in body positivity'
OL,6,FFronting the cover of Elle UK's April
OL,7,Fissue, Coughlan told the magazine:
OL,8,F"The thing I say sometimes that pisses
OL,9,Fpeople off is I have no interest in
OL,10,Fbody positivity.
OL,12,F"When I was a kid growing up, I never
OL,13,Fthought about that. I didn't look at
OL,14,Factors and think about their bodies.
OL,15,FSo, I actually don't care.
OL,17,F"There's a lot of things I'm
OL,18,Fpassionate about, it's not one of
OL,19,Fthem... That's someone else's thing.
OL,20,FIt's not mine."
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU|D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
