OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772679804
OL,3,CBridgerton star Nicola Coughlan has
OL,4,C'no interest in body positivity'
OL,6,FThe actress added that despite being a
OL,7,Fsize 10, she will still be praised as
OL,8,Fsomeone who appears on screen as a
OL,9,Fplus-size actress, comments which she
OL,10,Ffinds "boring".
OL,12,FSpeaking about the reaction to her
OL,13,Fnude scenes on the show, she said:
OL,14,F"What was really bizarre was when I
OL,15,Fwas shooting that series, I was
OL,16,Fexercising a lot because I knew I had
OL,17,Fto, so I had lost a bunch of weight `
OL,18,FI was probably a size 10 and one of
OL,19,Fthe corsets was a size 8.
OL,26,@rD@GOUrD@NO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
