PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772679804
OL,3,CBridgerton star Nicola Coughlan has
OL,4,C'no interest in body positivity'
OL,6,F"Then people talked about how I was
OL,7,Fplus size and I was like, 'How f*****
OL,8,Fare we that I am the biggest woman you
OL,9,Fwant to see on screen?'
OL,11,F"I remember this really drunk girl
OL,12,Fonce talking to me in a bathroom being
OL,13,Flike, 'I loved (Bridgerton) because of
OL,14,Fyour body' and started talking about
OL,15,Fmy body, and I was like, 'I want to
OL,16,Fdie. I hate this so much'.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
