OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772679804
OL,3,CBridgerton star Nicola Coughlan has
OL,4,C'no interest in body positivity'
OL,6,F"It's really hard when you work on
OL,7,Fsomething for months and months of
OL,8,Fyour life, you don't see your family,
OL,9,Fyou really dedicate yourself and then
OL,10,Fit comes down to what you look like `
OL,11,Fit's so f****** boring."
OL,13,FCoughlan also told the magazine that
OL,14,Fshe gives herself more "grace" since
OL,15,Freceiving her ADHD diagnosis.
OL,17,FShe said: "It feels like I got the
OL,18,Fhandbook to my brain that I wasn't
OL,19,Fgiven when I was born.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@XO]vD@XOUvD@^O]yD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
