PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1772679804
OL,3,CBridgerton star Nicola Coughlan has
OL,4,C'no interest in body positivity'
OL,6,F"I understand things a bit better now,
OL,7,Fand I give myself a little more grace."
OL,9,FCoughlan is also known for starring in
OL,10,Fthe hit movie Barbie as well as
OL,11,FChannel 4's Big Mood, a role which
OL,12,Fsecured her a Bafta nomination.
OL,14,FShe also appeared in a National
OL,15,FTheatre production of The Playboy Of
OL,16,FThe Western World alongside her Derry
OL,17,FGirls co-star Siobhan McSweeney.
OL,19,FThe full interview can be read in the
OL,20,FApril issue of Elle UK, which goes on
OL,21,Fsale on March 10.
